HEADWORD: Rearrange
<hw>Re`ar*range"</hw></mhw>
<pr>(r⟦emac⟧`⟦acr⟧r*r⟦amac⟧nj")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To arrange
again; to put into a different order; to arrange in a different way;
<as>as, Please <ex>re-arrange</ex> these files in alphabetical
order</as>. Usually used without the hyphen.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

